---
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';

const metadata = {
  title: 'Skills — Demetri Williams',
};
---

<Layout metadata={metadata}>
  <section class="px-6 py-12 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-2">Skills & Technologies</h1>
    <p class="text-muted mb-10">A blend of AI/ML knowledge, full-stack development, and data analysis built through coursework, projects, and real-world experience.</p>

    <div class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">AI & Machine Learning</h2>
      <p class="text-muted">Reinforcement learning, neural networks, model training & fine-tuning, LLMs, PyTorch, and working with real-world datasets. Hands-on experience training and evaluating AI models professionally at TELUS Digital and Outlier AI.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">Full-Stack Development</h2>
      <p class="text-muted">Python (Flask), JavaScript, HTML/CSS, Firebase, REST APIs, and building end-to-end web applications. Built full-stack projects including a Steam API integration with leaderboards and dashboards.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">Data & Analytics</h2>
      <p class="text-muted">SQL, data analysis, reporting, dashboards, Google Analytics, and translating raw data into actionable insights. Experience preparing detailed data reports for engineering teams nationally and internationally.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">Cloud & DevOps</h2>
      <p class="text-muted">AWS, Google Cloud, Azure, Linux, Bash scripting, and cloud infrastructure fundamentals. Coursework in Introduction to Cloud Computing at LSU, and the rest is self taught.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">Programming Languages</h2>
      <p class="text-muted">Python, Java, C, C++, C#, SQL, JavaScript, Bash; comfortable across multiple paradigms and programming environments.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">Design & Collaboration</h2>
      <p class="text-muted">Figma, hi-fi/lo-fi UI/UX design, Scrum, cross-functional teamwork, and technical documentation. Experience collaborating with teams internationally and presenting findings to engineering colleagues.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>